title: Did Elon Musk Donald Trump call Dombas?
subtitle: Unlike a fabricated tweet, the Executive Director of Space X gently responded to Trump's congratulations on the "American ingenuity" of the heavy hawk rocket.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In response to Donald Trump's congratulations on the launch of the Heavy Hawk, the CEO of SpaceX (Elon Mask) called the President Dombas.
